      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "That throws an exception, because <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/time/Duration.html#between-java.time.temporal.Temporal-java.time.temporal.Temporal-\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">the Duration.between method requires temporal objects capable of supporting the SECONDS unit</a>.  Instead, try <code>Duration.between(today.atTime(0, 0), yesterday.atTime(0, 0)).toDays()</code>."
