    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<blockquote>\n  <p>get days between two dates date is instance of java.util.Date</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n<pre><code>public static long daysBetweenTwoDates(Date dateFrom, Date dateTo) {\n            return DAYS.between(Instant.ofEpochMilli(dateFrom.getTime()), Instant.ofEpochMilli(dateTo.getTime()));\n        }\n</code></pre>\n"
