    "question_id" : 27005861,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I know this question is for Java 8, but with Java 9 you could use:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static List&lt;LocalDate&gt; getDatesBetween(LocalDate startDate, LocalDate endDate) {\n    return startDate.datesUntil(endDate)\n      .collect(Collectors.toList());\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
